{"tid":863172,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈價成交】康怡花園終開齋! 兩房減價110萬易手","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T14:43:33.000Z","uid":174649,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ef3a4b2fdd4f7efb4ab17e6a49e5c299451c50","tid":863172,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"中原地產楊文傑表示，鰂魚涌康怡花園終打破兩個月以來零成交悶局，業主面對現實劈價沽貨。劈價貨為N座高層15室，實用面積466方呎，2房間隔。業主叫價960萬元，最終劈價110萬元以850萬元將單位易手，呎價18,240元，是次成交價返回3月成交價。同類高位成交為P座高層14室，實用面積466方呎，今年7月造價900萬元，呎價19,313元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主1991年3月以127萬元買入單位，持貨27年，賬面獲利723萬元，單位升值5.7倍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181015/large/1539586615_008e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181015%2Flarge%2F1539586615_008e.jpg&h=b5919c08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"041f1b2ab6e6f9387217994ff6d691b06a1c6d15","tid":863172,"uid":195728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"賺左5倍又賺住，唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca24eb4c0a3d17f363b91e9c4b8a3edea0e2057b","tid":863172,"uid":171446,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81902649944c13edb378e72d523f4cd0869b42f5","tid":863172,"uid":84054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"荃灣先計 太古唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5957323ce3d6c0f325a99b79dd46b556d7e68def","tid":863172,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd45eb947373912832ad45dd865bfd73234cb347","tid":863172,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5957323ce3d6c0f325a99b79dd46b556d7e68def","tid":863172,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"cit